{"type": "article", "id": 4253, "title": "Christian Rich x L.G.R.联名太阳镜", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-10T07:52:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135250XHS8qOjevZy7ME4C.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利顶级眼镜品牌 L.G.R. 日前联手双胞胎兄弟 Taiwo Hassan 与 Kehinde Hassan 组成的 DJ 二人组 Christian Rich ，推出了一款联名太阳镜，以 L.G.R. 经典的 Cape Town 眼镜的轮廓为基础，选用了亚光磨砂黑色的纤维材质镜框，搭配深绿色矿物材质的镜片，纯手工制作而成，并在眼镜上印上了 Christian Rich 的logo。平直的眼镜顶部线条配以圆圆的镜框，赋予了这款眼镜独特的性格。这款联名产品将于本月 19 日正式发售，定价 308 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.lgrworld.com/shop/cape-town-special-edition/lgr-for-christian-rich/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试预定</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135248pSzxoPrRTkwC8dJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061352488AhYEy7I3wH5ZVpm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135249NmGl8C1aOSWveFTH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}